  <brief_title>GLPG0259 Solid Formulation Bioavailability and Food Effect</brief_title>
  <official_title>An Open Label Study to Compare the Oral Bioavailability of a Solid Dose Formulation of GLPG0259 Relative to an Oral Solution After Single-dose Intake in Healthy Subjects and to Evaluate the Effect of Food on the Solid Dose Formulation.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
