  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to compare the pharmacokinetics of GLPG0259 as a solid dosage
      formulation (with and without food)and an oral solution, and to assess its safety and
      tolerability.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
